[
  {
    "content_id": 1508001001,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;當士師秉政的時候，國中遭遇饑荒。在 猶大的 伯利恆，有一個人帶着妻子和兩個兒子往 摩押地去寄居。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001002,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;這人名叫 以利米勒，他的妻名叫 拿俄米；他兩個兒子，一個名叫 瑪倫，一個名叫 基連，都是 猶大 伯利恆的 以法他人。他們到了 摩押地，就住在那裏。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001003,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;後來 拿俄米的丈夫 以利米勒死了，剩下婦人和她兩個兒子。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001004,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>4</sup>&nbsp;這兩個兒子娶了 摩押女子為妻，一個名叫 俄珥巴，一個名叫 路得，在那裏住了約有十年。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001005,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>5</sup>&nbsp;瑪倫和 基連二人也死了，剩下 拿俄米，沒有丈夫，也沒有兒子。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001006,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>6</sup>&nbsp;她就與兩個兒婦起身，要從 摩押地歸回；因為她在 摩押地聽見耶和華眷顧自己的百姓，賜糧食與他們。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001007,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>7</sup>&nbsp;於是她和兩個兒婦起行離開所住的地方，要回 猶大地去。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001008,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>8</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米對兩個兒婦說：「你們各人回娘家去吧。願耶和華恩待你們，像你們恩待已死的人與我一樣！</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001009,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>9</sup>&nbsp;願耶和華使你們各在新夫家中得平安！」於是 拿俄米與她們親嘴。她們就放聲而哭，</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001010,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>10</sup>&nbsp;說：「不然，我們必與你一同回你本國去。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001011,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>11</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米說：「我女兒們哪，回去吧！為何要跟我去呢？我還能生子作你們的丈夫嗎？</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001012,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>12</sup>&nbsp;我女兒們哪，回去吧！我年紀老邁，不能再有丈夫；即或說，我還有指望，今夜有丈夫可以生子，</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001013,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>13</sup>&nbsp;你們豈能等着他們長大呢？你們豈能等着他們不嫁別人呢？我女兒們哪，不要這樣。我為你們的緣故甚是愁苦，因為耶和華伸手攻擊我。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001014,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>14</sup>&nbsp;兩個兒婦又放聲而哭， 俄珥巴與婆婆親嘴 而別，只是 路得捨不得 拿俄米。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001015,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>15</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米說：「看哪，你嫂子已經回她本國和她 所拜的神那裏去了，你也跟着你嫂子回去吧！」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001016,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>16</sup>&nbsp;路得說：「不要催我回去不跟隨你。你往哪裏去，我也往那裏去；你在哪裏住宿，我也在那裏住宿；你的國就是我的國，你的神就是我的神。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001017,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>17</sup>&nbsp;你在哪裏死，我也在那裏死，也葬在那裏。除非死能使你我相離！不然，願耶和華重重地降罰與我。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001018,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>18</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米見 路得定意要跟隨自己去，就不再勸她了。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001019,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>19</sup>&nbsp;於是二人同行，來到 伯利恆。她們到了 伯利恆，合城的人就都驚訝。婦女們說：「這是 拿俄米嗎？」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001020,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>20</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米對她們說：「不要叫我 拿俄米，要叫我 瑪拉，因為全能者使我受了大苦。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001021,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>21</sup>&nbsp;我滿滿地出去，耶和華使我空空地回來。耶和華降禍與我；全能者使我受苦。既是這樣，你們為何還叫我 拿俄米呢？」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508001022,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>22</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米和她兒婦 摩押女子 路得，從 摩押地回來到 伯利恆，正是動手割大麥的時候。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002001,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米的丈夫 以利米勒的親族中，有一個人名叫 波阿斯，是個大財主。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002002,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;摩押女子 路得對 拿俄米說：「容我往田間去，我蒙誰的恩，就在誰的身後拾取麥穗。」 拿俄米說：「女兒啊，你只管去。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002003,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;路得就去了，來到田間，在收割的人身後拾取麥穗。她恰巧到了 以利米勒本族的人 波阿斯那塊田裏。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002004,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>4</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯正從 伯利恆來，對收割的人說：「願耶和華與你們同在！」他們回答說：「願耶和華賜福與你！」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002005,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>5</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯問監管收割的僕人說：「那是誰家的女子？」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002006,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>6</sup>&nbsp;監管收割的僕人回答說：「是那 摩押女子，跟隨 拿俄米從 摩押地回來的。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002007,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>7</sup>&nbsp;她說：『請你容我跟着收割的人拾取打捆剩下的麥穗。』她從早晨直到如今，除了在屋子裏坐一會兒，常在這裏。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002008,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>8</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯對 路得說：「女兒啊，聽我說，不要往別人田裏拾取麥穗，也不要離開這裏，要常與我使女們在一處。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002009,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>9</sup>&nbsp;我的僕人在那塊田收割，你就跟着他們去。我已經吩咐僕人不可欺負你；你若渴了，就可以到器皿那裏喝僕人打來的水。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002010,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>10</sup>&nbsp;路得就俯伏在地叩拜，對他說：「我既是外邦人，怎麼蒙你的恩，這樣顧恤我呢？」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002011,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>11</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯回答說：「自從你丈夫死後，凡你向婆婆所行的，並你離開父母和本地，到素不認識的民中，這些事人全都告訴我了。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002012,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>12</sup>&nbsp;願耶和華照你所行的賞賜你。你來投靠耶和華－ 以色列神的翅膀下，願你滿得他的賞賜。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002013,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>13</sup>&nbsp;路得說：「我主啊，願在你眼前蒙恩。我雖然不及你的一個使女，你還用慈愛的話安慰我的心。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002014,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>14</sup>&nbsp;到了吃飯的時候， 波阿斯對 路得說：「你到這裏來吃餅，將餅蘸在醋裏。」 路得就在收割的人旁邊坐下；他們把烘了的穗子遞給她。她吃飽了，還有餘剩的。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002015,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>15</sup>&nbsp;她起來又拾取麥穗， 波阿斯吩咐僕人說：「她就是在捆中拾取麥穗，也可以容她，不可羞辱她；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002016,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>16</sup>&nbsp;並要從捆裏抽出些來，留在地下任她拾取，不可叱嚇她。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002017,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>17</sup>&nbsp;這樣， 路得在田間拾取麥穗，直到晚上，將所拾取的打了，約有一伊法大麥。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002018,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>18</sup>&nbsp;她就把所拾取的帶進城去給婆婆看，又把她吃飽了所剩的給了婆婆。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002019,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002019",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>19</sup>&nbsp;婆婆問她說：「你今日在哪裏拾取麥穗，在哪裏做工呢？願那顧恤你的得福。」 路得就告訴婆婆說：「我今日在一個名叫 波阿斯的人那裏做工。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002020,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>20</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米對兒婦說：「願那人蒙耶和華賜福，因為他不斷地恩待活人死人。」 拿俄米又說：「那是我們本族的人，是一個至近的親屬。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002021,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002021",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>21</sup>&nbsp;摩押女子 路得說：「他對我說：『你要緊隨我的僕人 拾取麥穗，直等他們收完了我的莊稼。』」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002022,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>22</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米對兒婦 路得說：「女兒啊，你跟着他的使女出去，不叫人遇見你在別人田間，這才為好。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508002023,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 2:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002023",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>23</sup>&nbsp;於是 路得與 波阿斯的使女常在一處拾取麥穗，直到收完了大麥和小麥。 路得仍與婆婆同住。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003001,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;路得的婆婆 拿俄米對她說：「女兒啊，我不當為你找個安身之處，使你享福嗎？</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003002,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;你與 波阿斯的使女常在一處， 波阿斯不是我們的親族嗎？他今夜在場上簸大麥；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003003,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;你要沐浴抹膏，換上衣服，下到場上，卻不要使那人認出你來。你等他吃喝完了，</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003004,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>4</sup>&nbsp;到他睡的時候，你看準他睡的地方，就進去掀開他腳上的被，躺臥在那裏，他必告訴你所當做的事。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003005,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>5</sup>&nbsp;路得說：「凡你所吩咐的，我必遵行。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003006,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>6</sup>&nbsp;路得就下到場上，照她婆婆所吩咐她的而行。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003007,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>7</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯吃喝完了，心裏歡暢，就去睡在麥堆旁邊。 路得便悄悄地來掀開他腳上的被，躺臥在那裏。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003008,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>8</sup>&nbsp;到了夜半，那人忽然驚醒，翻過身來，不料有女子躺在他的腳下。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003009,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>9</sup>&nbsp;他就說：「你是誰？」回答說：「我是你的婢女 路得。求你用你的衣襟遮蓋我，因為你是我一個至近的親屬。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003010,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>10</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯說：「女兒啊，願你蒙耶和華賜福。你末後的恩比先前更大；因為少年人無論貧富，你都沒有跟從。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003011,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>11</sup>&nbsp;女兒啊，現在不要懼怕，凡你所說的，我必照着行；我本城的人都知道你是個賢德的女子。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003012,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>12</sup>&nbsp;我實在是你一個至近的親屬，只是還有一個人比我更近。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003013,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>13</sup>&nbsp;你今夜在這裏住宿，明早他若肯為你盡親屬的本分，就由他吧！倘若不肯，我指着永生的耶和華起誓，我必為你盡了本分，你只管躺到天亮。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003014,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>14</sup>&nbsp;路得便在他腳下躺到天快亮，人彼此不能辨認的時候就起來了。 波阿斯說：「不可使人知道有女子到場上來」；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003015,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>15</sup>&nbsp;又對 路得說：「打開你所披的外衣。」她打開了， 波阿斯就撮了六 簸箕大麥，幫她扛在肩上，她便進城去了。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003016,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>16</sup>&nbsp;路得回到婆婆那裏，婆婆說：「女兒啊，怎麼樣了？」 路得就將那人向她所行的述說了一遍，</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003017,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>17</sup>&nbsp;又說：「那人給了我六 簸箕大麥，對我說：『你不可空手回去見你的婆婆。』」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508003018,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 3:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>18</sup>&nbsp;婆婆說：「女兒啊，你只管安坐等候，看這事怎樣成就，因為那人今日不辦成這事必不休息。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004001,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯到了城門，坐在那裏，恰巧 波阿斯所說的那至近的親屬經過。 波阿斯說：「某人哪，你來坐在這裏。」他就來坐下。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004002,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯又從本城的長老中揀選了十人，對他們說：「請你們坐在這裏。」他們就都坐下。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004003,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯對那至近的親屬說：「從 摩押地回來的 拿俄米，現在要賣我們族兄 以利米勒的那塊地；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004004,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>4</sup>&nbsp;我想當贖那塊地的是你，其次是我，以外再沒有別人了。你可以在這裏的人面前和我本國的長老面前說明，你若肯贖就贖，若不肯贖就告訴我。」那人回答說：「我肯贖。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004005,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>5</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯說：「你從 拿俄米手中買這地的時候，也當娶死人的妻 摩押女子 路得，使死人在產業上存留他的名。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004006,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004006",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>6</sup>&nbsp;那人說：「這樣我就不能贖了，恐怕於我的產業有礙。你可以贖我所當贖的，我不能贖了。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004007,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>7</sup>&nbsp;從前，在 以色列中要定奪甚麼事，或贖回，或交易，這人就脫鞋給那人。 以色列人都以此為證據。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004008,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>8</sup>&nbsp;那人對 波阿斯說：「你自己買吧！」於是將鞋脫下來了。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004009,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>9</sup>&nbsp;波阿斯對長老和眾民說：「你們今日作見證，凡屬 以利米勒和 基連、 瑪倫的，我都從 拿俄米手中置買了；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004010,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004010",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>10</sup>&nbsp;又娶了 瑪倫的妻 摩押女子 路得為妻，好在死人的產業上存留他的名，免得他的名在本族本鄉滅沒。你們今日可以作見證。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004011,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>11</sup>&nbsp;在城門坐着的眾民和長老都說：「我們作見證。願耶和華使進你家的這女子，像建立 以色列家的 拉結、 利亞二人一樣。又願你在 以法他得亨通，在 伯利恆得名聲。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004012,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>12</sup>&nbsp;願耶和華從這少年女子賜你後裔，使你的家像 她瑪從 猶大所生 法勒斯的家一般。」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004013,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004013",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>13</sup>&nbsp;於是， 波阿斯娶了 路得為妻，與她同房。耶和華使她懷孕生了一個兒子。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004014,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>14</sup>&nbsp;婦人們對 拿俄米說：「耶和華是應當稱頌的！因為今日沒有撇下你，使你無至近的親屬。願這孩子在 以色列中得名聲。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004015,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>15</sup>&nbsp;他必提起你的精神，奉養你的老，因為是愛慕你的那兒婦所生的。有這兒婦比有七個兒子還好！」</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004016,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>16</sup>&nbsp;拿俄米就把孩子抱在懷中，作他的養母。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004017,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>17</sup>&nbsp;鄰舍的婦人說：「 拿俄米得孩子了！」就給孩子起名叫 俄備得。這 俄備得是 耶西的父， 耶西是 大衛的父。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004018,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>18</sup>&nbsp;法勒斯的後代記在下面： 法勒斯生 希斯崙；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004019,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004019",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>19</sup>&nbsp;希斯崙生 蘭； 蘭生 亞米拿達；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004020,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004020",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>20</sup>&nbsp;亞米拿達生 拿順； 拿順生 撒門；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004021,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004021",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>21</sup>&nbsp;撒門生 波阿斯； 波阿斯生 俄備得；</p>",
    "associations": {}
  },
  {
    "content_id": 1508004022,
    "reference_id": null,
    "version": "1.0.2",
    "title": "Ruth 4:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08004022",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><sup>22</sup>&nbsp;俄備得生 耶西； 耶西生 大衛。</p>",
    "associations": {}
  }
]